# GoPool Main Features

## 1. User Authentication
- Login
- Sign-up
- Password recovery

## 2. Ride Management
- Post a ride
- Search for rides
- View ride details

## 3. Booking System
- Book a ride
- Cancel booking

## 4. Payment Integration
- Online payment options
- Payment confirmation

## 5. Ratings and Reviews
- Rate drivers
- Post and view reviews
